name.value: Care Connect SDS Job Role Name

description.value: A set of RBAC codes to indicate the job role associated with the person on the smart card. This code list is externally maintained.

requirements.value: This ValueSet has an inline code system: 'https://fhir.hl7.org.uk/CareConnect-SDSJobRoleName-1'.
